steps: Click on the 'File' tab in the top left corner.
Select the 'Print' option from the dropdown menu.
Choose the desired printer from the list of available printers.
Specify the number of copies you want to print.
Select any additional print settings, such as page range or paper size.
Click on the 'Print' button to start printing the document.
Wait for the document to be printed.
Verify that the document has been successfully printed.
